ActFirst Nations Fiscal and Statistical Management Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the First Nations Fiscal and Statistical Management Act
PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE FIRST NATIONS FISCAL AND STATISTICAL MANAGEMENT ACT by adding eleven First Nations, in order to allow them to access the full array of services available through the First Nation institutions created under the Act.
